# DOE Kit: project-specific term blocklist
# Used by execution/audit_sync.py to skip project-specific files from
# the universal-sync detection. One term per line. Lines starting with
# `#` are comments. Matched case-insensitively as `\bWORD\b` regex.
#
# Copy this file to `.kit-blocklist` (gitignored) and add your project's
# codenames, domain terms, and file-path fragments. Each clone of the
# kit has its own list -- nothing here ships across consumers.
#
# Examples (delete and replace with your actual terms):
# myproject
# acme-app
# specific-domain-term
